@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Archived
Archived --> Cancelled : submit
Archived : entry / log checkin
Cancelled --> Completed : update
Cancelled : entry / log checkin
Completed --> Pending : cancel
Completed : entry / log checkin
Pending --> Closed : approve
Pending : entry / log checkin
Pending --> Completed : revert
Closed --> [*]
@enduml